query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS withdrawalLimits (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  userId INT NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  dailyLimit DECIMAL(20,8) DEFAULT 10000 NOT NULL,
  monthlyLimit DECIMAL(20,8) DEFAULT 100000 NOT NULL,
  dailyUsed DECIMAL(20,8) DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  monthlyUsed DECIMAL(20,8) DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  lastDailyReset TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  lastMonthlyReset TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
